OL,3,GEast
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA grey start for most with
OL,6,Fareas of low cloud and some patchy
OL,7,Flight rain in places. However, cloud
OL,8,Fgradually lifting and thinning inland
OL,9,Fwith some breaks developing later.
OL,10,FMostly dry, although isolated light
OL,11,Fshowers likely. Light winds.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FVariable cloud with some
OL,14,Fbreaks, and patchy mist, fog or low
OL,15,Fcloud likely to develop in places.
OL,16,FWinds remaining light.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
