OL,3,GEast
OL,4,
OL,5,CTuesday:FBright or sunny spells but
OL,6,Fturning cloudier towards evening as
OL,7,Fscattered showers move south, with a
OL,8,Fcooler northerly breeze arriving
OL,9,Fovernight.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FBright
OL,12,For sunny spells and a chance of
OL,13,Fisolated, mainly light showers each
OL,14,Fday. Cooler midweek, with patchy
OL,15,Fovernight rural grass frost possible,
OL,16,Fturning milder again later. Winds
OL,17,Fgenerally light.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
